# Gravity
## What's it do
Simulates a particle field and is currently beig worked on to create random systems.
## Authors and Contributors
[Taken from Ian Mallet's work on Gravitation](http://geometrian.com/programming/projects/index.php?project=Gravitation)

This fork of Gravitation is called Gravity and is worked on and maintained by:
- @Toggle2
- @KnightHawk3
